[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 - Audition Guidelines]

• Day 1 (September 15, 2025): Pavilion 2
• Day 2 & 3 (September 16-17, 2025): ARH 302-303

📌 We also accept walk-ins! So lock and load your talents and get ready to shine!

Best of luck, performers! 🔰

[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 - Audition Guidelines]

The mission briefing is in: here are the guidelines for this year's TamHunt auditions. 
Gear up and get ready to deploy your skills!

🗓️ 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗗𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀: September 15-17, 2025 (6:00 PM - 8:30 PM)

• Day 1 (September 15, 2025): Pavilion 2
• Day 2 & 3 (September 16-17, 2025): ARH 302-303

📌 We also accept walk-ins! So lock and load your talents and get ready to shine!

Best of luck, performers! 🔰

𝗔𝗟𝗟 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧𝗦, 𝗥𝗘𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗙𝗢𝗥 𝗗𝗨𝗧𝗬! 📣

The mission briefing is in: here are the guidelines for this year's TamHunt auditions. 
Gear up and get ready to deploy your skills!

🗓️ 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗗𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀: September 15-17, 2025 (6:00 PM - 8:30 PM)
📍 𝗩𝗲𝗻𝘂𝗲𝘀: 
• Day 1 (September 15, 2025): Pavilion 2
• Day 2 & 3 (September 16-17, 2025): ARH 302-303
👤 𝗧𝗮𝗿𝗴𝗲𝘁 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲: Open to All FEU–ITHM Students
🔗 𝗟𝗶𝗻𝗸 𝗼𝗳 𝗥𝗲𝗴𝗶𝘀𝘁𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗙𝗼𝗿𝗺: https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 We also accept walk-ins! So lock and load your talents and get ready to shine!

Best of luck, performers! 🔰

Pubmat By:
Hisami Muramatsu
Ian Canlas

Caption By: Mae Saeed

message.text:
🎓✨𝙏𝙤 𝙖 𝙗𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙣𝙣𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙤𝙛 𝙜𝙧𝙚𝙖𝙩𝙚𝙧 𝙩𝙧𝙞𝙪𝙢𝙥𝙝𝙨, 𝘾𝙤𝙣𝙜𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙡𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣𝙨!✨🎓

Hats off to you, Doctor! Your success is a powerful mix of grit, brilliance, and unstoppable determination. Earning your PhD is no small feat, and you’ve proven that perseverance truly pays off. May this milestone signal the start of new chances where your expertise and enthusiasm will continue to shine, in addition to the end of countless sleepless nights and unending research.

To our FEU Guidance and Counseling Director, 𝗗𝗿. 𝗛𝗮𝗿𝗱𝗶𝗲 𝗚𝗶𝗲𝗯𝗲𝗻 𝗖𝗿𝘂𝘇, you have our admiration and we hope you continue to have a significant influence on your field and the lives of many others. 𝗟𝗲𝘁'𝘀 𝘁𝗼𝗮𝘀𝘁 𝘁𝗼 𝗳𝗿𝗲𝘀𝗵 𝘀𝘁𝗮𝗿𝘁𝘀 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗺𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗮𝗰𝗵𝗶𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁𝘀 𝗶𝗻 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗳𝘂𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗲! 🥂👏

#DoubleOnes
#AboutYouAndUs
#KindnessAndCompassion
#FEUABCG

Caption by Jesster P. Batapa
Publication Material by Angelika Lazaro

message.text:
🎓✨𝙏𝙤 𝙖 𝙗𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙣𝙣𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙤𝙛 𝙜𝙧𝙚𝙖𝙩𝙚𝙧 𝙩𝙧𝙞𝙪𝙢𝙥𝙝𝙨, 𝘾𝙤𝙣𝙜𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙡𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣𝙨!✨🎓

Hats off to you, Doctor! Your success is a powerful mix of grit, brilliance, and unstoppable determination. Earning your PhD is no small feat, and you’ve proven that perseverance truly pays off. May this milestone signal the start of new chances where your expertise and enthusiasm will continue to shine, in addition to the end of countless sleepless nights and unending research.

To our FEU Guidance and Counseling Director, 𝗗𝗿. 𝗛𝗮𝗿𝗱𝗶𝗲 𝗚𝗶𝗲𝗯𝗲𝗻 𝗖𝗿𝘂𝘇, you have our admiration and we hope you continue to have a significant influence on your field and the lives of many others. 𝗟𝗲𝘁'𝘀 𝘁𝗼𝗮𝘀𝘁 𝘁𝗼 𝗳𝗿𝗲𝘀𝗵 𝘀𝘁𝗮𝗿𝘁𝘀 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗺𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗮𝗰𝗵𝗶𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁𝘀 𝗶𝗻 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗳𝘂𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗲! 🥂👏

#DoubleOnes
#AboutYouAndUs
#KindnessAndCompassion
#FEUABCG

message.text:
🎓✨𝙏𝙤 𝙖 𝙗𝙚𝙜𝙞𝙣𝙣𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙤𝙛 𝙜𝙧𝙚𝙖𝙩𝙚𝙧 𝙩𝙧𝙞𝙪𝙢𝙥𝙝𝙨, 𝘾𝙤𝙣𝙜𝙧𝙖𝙩𝙪𝙡𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣𝙨!✨🎓

Hats off to you, Doctor! Your success is a powerful mix of grit, brilliance, and unstoppable determination. Earning your PhD is no small feat, and you’ve proven that perseverance truly pays off. May this milestone signal the start of new chances where your expertise and enthusiasm will continue to shine, in addition to the end of countless sleepless nights and unending research.

To our FEU Guidance and Counseling Director, 𝗗𝗿. 𝗛𝗮𝗿𝗱𝗶𝗲 𝗚𝗶𝗲𝗯𝗲𝗻 𝗖𝗿𝘂𝘇, you have our admiration and we hope you continue to have a significant influence on your field and the lives of many others. 𝗟𝗲𝘁'𝘀 𝘁𝗼𝗮𝘀𝘁 𝘁𝗼 𝗳𝗿𝗲𝘀𝗵 𝘀𝘁𝗮𝗿𝘁𝘀 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗺𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗮𝗰𝗵𝗶𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁𝘀 𝗶𝗻 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗳𝘂𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗲! 🥂👏

#DoubleOnes
#AboutYouAndUs
#KindnessAndCompassion
#FEUABCG

Caption by Jesster P. Batapa
Publication Material by Angelika Lazaro

𝙣𝙖𝙣-𝙉𝙄Ñ𝙊 𝙖𝙠𝙤, 𝙪𝙢𝙞𝙞𝙗𝙞𝙜 𝙨𝙖𝙮𝙤…𝙥𝙚𝙧𝙤 𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙙𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙙𝙞 𝙢𝙖𝙙𝙪𝙙𝙪𝙧𝙤𝙜 𝙖𝙣𝙜 𝙥𝙪𝙨𝙤. 🥰💗

Happy birthday to our ever-reliable Business Manager, 𝐍𝐢ñ𝐨 𝐌𝐜 𝐀𝐧𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐧𝐲 𝐒. 𝐁𝐨𝐫𝐣𝐚, a figure of quiet strength and unwavering dedication in everything he takes on. Like the 𝘀𝗮𝗽𝗽𝗵𝗶𝗿𝗲, he stands firm and grounded. He carries wisdom and a quiet brilliance that shines in every challenge.

𝗬𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗔𝗕𝗖𝗚 𝗳𝗮𝗺𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝗰𝗲𝗹𝗲𝗯𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀 𝘆𝗼𝘂 — for the dedication that drives your work and the quiet strength that inspires those around you. 

𝗠𝗮𝘆 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗰𝗼𝗺𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘆𝗲𝗮𝗿 𝗯𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗲𝘅𝗽𝗮𝗻𝘀𝗶𝗼𝗻, 𝘀𝘂𝗰𝗰𝗲𝘀𝘀, 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗺𝗼𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁𝘀 𝘁𝗵𝗮𝘁 𝗿𝗲𝗳𝗹𝗲𝗰𝘁 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗵𝗲𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗽𝘂𝘁 𝗶𝗻 𝗮𝗹𝗹 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗱𝗼. 💎🌟

message.text:
𝙣𝙖𝙣-𝙉𝙄Ñ𝙊 𝙖𝙠𝙤, 𝙪𝙢𝙞𝙞𝙗𝙞𝙜 𝙨𝙖𝙮𝙤…𝙥𝙚𝙧𝙤 𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙙𝙞𝙣𝙜 𝙝𝙞𝙣𝙙𝙞 𝙢𝙖𝙙𝙪𝙙𝙪𝙧𝙤𝙜 𝙖𝙣𝙜 𝙥𝙪𝙨𝙤. 🥰💗

Happy birthday to our ever-reliable Business Manager, 𝐍𝐢ñ𝐨 𝐌𝐜 𝐀𝐧𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐧𝐲 𝐒. 𝐁𝐨𝐫𝐣𝐚, a figure of quiet strength and unwavering dedication in everything he takes on. Like the 𝘀𝗮𝗽𝗽𝗵𝗶𝗿𝗲, he stands firm and grounded. He carries wisdom and a quiet brilliance that shines in every challenge.

𝗬𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗔𝗕𝗖𝗚 𝗳𝗮𝗺𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝗰𝗲𝗹𝗲𝗯𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗲𝘀 𝘆𝗼𝘂 — for the dedication that drives your work and the quiet strength that inspires those around you. 

𝗠𝗮𝘆 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗰𝗼𝗺𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘆𝗲𝗮𝗿 𝗯𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗲𝘅𝗽𝗮𝗻𝘀𝗶𝗼𝗻, 𝘀𝘂𝗰𝗰𝗲𝘀𝘀, 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗺𝗼𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁𝘀 𝘁𝗵𝗮𝘁 𝗿𝗲𝗳𝗹𝗲𝗰𝘁 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗵𝗲𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗽𝘂𝘁 𝗶𝗻 𝗮𝗹𝗹 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗱𝗼. 💎🌟

To the gem you are,
𝙔𝙤𝙪𝙧 𝘼𝘽𝘾𝙂 𝙁𝙖𝙢𝙞𝙡𝙮

#KindnessAndCompassion
#FEUABCG
